ComicInfo.Summary: As he travels across Oukoku, Dark, learns that the things are not always what they seem! Leen, the usually hot headed, hard bodied ruler of the Land of the West Wind does not want to rush into battle! And Kyo, Dark's companion and advisor, also seems to have had a sudden change of heart. Her timing couldn't be worse either as Dark is in for the fight of his life as a new villian enters the picture.
